_sText:
The map is a fight yard and it is for fun or practice with all weapons if you want. 

It's great for Lan Parties or servers online. The map is best with few people because with a lot of people the unlucky die quickly. 

There are a couple places to hide, but don't be a camper all the time okay!

This map is also great for a small group of people or just 1 friend.
